.modal(v-bind:class="{ 'is-active': showFaqModal }")
    .modal-background
    .modal-card
        header.modal-card-head
            p.modal-card-title Frequently Asked Questions/FAQ
            button.delete(aria-label='close' @click='toggleFaqModalVisibility')
        section.modal-card-body
            strong What is a privacy policy?
            p A legal document that explains how an organization collects, uses, shares, and protects personal data. It informs users about their privacy rights and how their information is handled.

            br
            strong What is personal data?
            p Any information that can identify a living individual, such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, IP addresses, or location data.

            br
            strong Why is a privacy policy important?
            p It builds trust with your users by being transparent about data practices. It also helps you comply with legal requirements and reduces the risk of penalties or disputes.

            br
            strong Is it safe to use a privacy policy template?
            p Yes, but it must be customized to reflect your specific practices. A template provides a solid starting point, but you should review it carefully and consult a lawyer to ensure it meets your legal obligations.

            br
            strong What are terms and conditions?
            p A legally binding agreement that defines the rules for using your app or service. It covers acceptable use, user rights and responsibilities, account termination, disclaimers, dispute resolution, and governing law.

            br
            strong Why is this tool free?
            p It was created to fill the need for a free, open-source alternative to paid privacy policy generators. The project is maintained in the developer's free time and supported by community contributions.
        footer.modal-card-foot
            button.button.is-info(aria-label='close' @click='toggleFaqModalVisibility')
